ine comparable expansion at more than 5.5%, driven by traffic and basket size. The company's margins did not expand, and it posted higher losses than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/148018060/image_148018060.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741874-citi-trends-impressive-q3-but-the-stock-has-discounted-a-full-turnaround", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 00:25:23"}, {"id": "4741872", "title": "AppLovin: Early Ecommerce Feedback Is Positive, But Expectations Are Enormous", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman playing a mobile racing game on a smartphone\" data-id=\"1445187539\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445187539/image_1445187539.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-